Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 12)

Package: f81601a-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms (>= 2.2.0.3), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fintek F81601A PCIe CAN kernel module (DKMS)
 This package contains the source for the Fintek F81601A
 PCIe CAN driver, packaged with DKMS to auto-rebuild on
 kernel upgrades. Supports up to 2 CAN channels.
